b-yP6h8gUz-0qSHd_H_szRLg=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering runtime initialization**\\n\\nI'm thinking about the tests under native runtime, as it seems they initialize by default. It looks like the existing report on line 146 covered that well, which is reassuring. Good to know! Now, it seems my next step is to create the necessary directories. I need to make sure I’m clear on what directories I need to set up to keep everything organized. Let's get that part sorted out!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_nzGNHgw2wZvaVdlF6g8ayrcj|fc_0a8b8711862d4de20169fc0e837a1c81918e6adbe7b140d467", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.mchange/c3p0/0.9.5.4/src/test/java/com_mchange/c3p0/C3P0RegistryTest.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage com_mchange.c3p0;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThatThrownBy;\n\nimport com.mchange.v2.c3p0.C3P0Registry;\nimport com.mchange.v2.c3p0.ConnectionTester;\nimport com.mchange.v2.c3p0.cfg.C3P0ConfigUtils;\nimport java.sql.SQLException;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\npublic class C3P0RegistryTest {\n    private static final String MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR_PROPERTY =\n            \"com.mchange.v2.c3p0.management.ManagementCoordinator\";\n    private static final String NULL_MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR =\n            \"com.mchange.v2.c3p0.management.NullManagementCoordinator\";\n    private static final String DEFAULT_CONNECTION_TESTER = \"com.mchange.v2.c3p0.impl.DefaultConnectionTester\";\n\n    @Test\n    void registryLoadsConfiguredManagementCoordinatorAndHandlesInvalidCustomTypes() {\n        assertThat(C3P0ConfigUtils.getPropsFileConfigProperty(MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR_PROPERTY))\n                .isEqualTo(NULL_MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR);\n\n        ConnectionTester fallbackTester = C3P0Registry.getConnectionTester(NULL_MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR);\n\n        assertThat(fallbackTester).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(fallbackTester.getClass().getName()).isEqualTo(DEFAULT_CONNECTION_TESTER);\n        assertThatThrownBy(() -> C3P0Registry.getConnectionCustomizer(NULL_MANAGEMENT_COORDINATOR))\n                .isInstanceOf(SQLException.class)\n                .hasCauseInstanceOf(ClassCastException.class);\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1882, "output": 1457, "cacheRead": 39424, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42763, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778126453114, "responseId": "resp_0a8b8711862d4de20169fc0e7592708191ad9d6cac6539e69e"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_nzGNHgw2wZvaVdlF6g8ayrcj|fc_0a8b8711862d4de20169fc0e837a1c81918e6adbe7b140d467", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1687 bytes to tests/src/com.mchange/c3p0/0.9.5.4/src/test/java/com_mchange/c3p0/C3P0RegistryTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778126471483}]}
